==主辦權==
2013年3月，國際曲總公佈2014-2018年週期賽程文件後的一個月，澳洲、比利時、印度、馬來西亞和紐西蘭入圍候選城市，須提交投標文件<ref>{{cite news|title=FIH Opens World Cup 2018 Bidding Process|url=http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4163-fih-opens-world-cup-2018-bidding-process|accessdate=2013-11-09|newspaper=FIH|date=2013-02-04|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109115732/http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4163-fih-opens-world-cup-2018-bidding-process|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Six nations shortlisted for Hockey World Cups 2018|url=http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4274-six-nations-shortlisted-for-hockey-world|accessdate=2013-11-09|newspaper=FIH|date=2013-03-18|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109115949/http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4274-six-nations-shortlisted-for-hockey-world|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最後比利時沒有完成。<ref>{{cite web|title=Five nations in battle to host FIH World Cups 2018|url=http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4720-five-nations-in-battle-to-host-fih-world|publisher=FIH|accessdate=2013-11-08|date=2013-09-10|archive-date=2018-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928234346/http://www.fih.ch/en/news-4720-five-nations-in-battle-to-host-fih-world|dead-url=no}}</ref>主辦權選舉前一個月澳洲因為技術和經濟因素退回申請。<ref>{{cite web|title=Four nations prepare to learn fate of 2018 Hockey World Cup bids|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/sports/summer/hockey/1016830-five-nations-prepare-to-learn-fate-of-2018-hockey-world-cup-bids|publisher=FIH|accessdate=2013-11-08|date=2013-11-06|archive-date=2014-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021053025/http://www.insidethegames.biz/sports/summer/hockey/1016830-five-nations-prepare-to-learn-fate-of-2018-hockey-world-cup-bids|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年11月7日，印度在瑞士洛桑舉行的特別儀式上獲得主辦權。

